<section id="conclusion" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="conclusion">Conclusion</h2>
<p>The four methods illuminate the same result from different angles: direct counting is concrete, shifting variables connects the problem to non-negative solutions, floor functions compress the count, and generating functions give a powerful general framework. Python verifies the final list.</p>
<p><img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/png.latex?%0A%5Cboxed%7B12%5Ctext%7B%20positive%20integer%20solutions%7D%7D.%0A"></p>
</section>
